{
  "id": "api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication",
  "title": "bootstrapApplication",
  "contents": "<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/platform-browser\", \"name\": \"@angular/platform-browser\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\", \"name\": \"bootstrapApplication\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/platform-browser\">@angular/platform-browser</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/platform-browser/src/browser.ts?message=docs(platform-browser)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L40-L129\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/14.1.0-next.0/packages/platform-browser/src/browser.ts#L40-L129\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"bootstrapapplication\">bootstrapApplication<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication#bootstrapapplication\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    <label class=\"api-status-label dev-preview\" title=\"This API is in Developer Preview\">\n      <a href=\"guide/releases#developer-preview\">developer preview</a>\n    </label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">引导 Angular\n应用程序的实例，并将独立组件呈现为应用程序的根组件。有关独立组件的更多信息，请参阅<a href=\"guide/standalone-components\">本指南</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Bootstraps an instance of an Angular application and renders a standalone component as the\napplication's root component. More information about standalone components can be found in <a href=\"guide/standalone-components\">this\nguide</a>.</p>\n\n\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a></span>(rootComponent: <a href=\"api/core/Type\" class=\"code-anchor\">Type</a>&#x3C;unknown>, options?: <a href=\"api/platform-browser/ApplicationConfig\" class=\"code-anchor\">ApplicationConfig</a>): Promise&#x3C;<a href=\"api/core/ApplicationRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ApplicationRef</a>></code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数\">参数</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>rootComponent</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/core/Type\" class=\"code-anchor\">Type</a>&#x3C;unknown></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">对应该呈现的独立组件的引用。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A reference to a standalone component that should be rendered.</p>\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>options</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/ApplicationConfig\" class=\"code-anchor\">ApplicationConfig</a></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">引导操作的额外配置，有关其他信息，请参阅 <code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/ApplicationConfig\" class=\"code-anchor\">ApplicationConfig</a></code> 。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Extra configuration for the bootstrap operation, see <code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/ApplicationConfig\" class=\"code-anchor\">ApplicationConfig</a></code> for\nadditional info.</p>\n\n\n        <p>可选值。默认值为 <code>undefined</code>。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h6>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">解析后返回 <code><a href=\"api/core/ApplicationRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ApplicationRef</a></code> 实例的 Promise。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>Promise&#x3C;<a href=\"api/core/ApplicationRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ApplicationRef</a>></code>: A promise that returns an <code><a href=\"api/core/ApplicationRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ApplicationRef</a></code> instance once resolved.</p>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">传递给此函数的根组件<em>必须</em>是独立的（在 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a></code> 装饰器配置中应该有 <code>standalone: true</code>\n标志）。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The root component passed into this function <em>must</em> be a standalone one (should have the\n<code>standalone: true</code> flag in the <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a></code> decorator config).</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a> ({\n  standalone: true,\n  template: 'Hello world!'\n})\nclass RootComponent {}\n\nconst appRef: <a href=\"api/core/ApplicationRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ApplicationRef</a> = await <a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a>(RootComponent);\n</code-example>\n<p>You can add the list of providers that should be available in the application injector by\nspecifying the <code>providers</code> field in an object passed as the second argument:</p>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nawait <a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a>(RootComponent, {\n  providers: [\n    {provide: BACKEND_URL, useValue: 'https://yourdomain.com/api'}\n  ]\n});\n</code-example>\n<p>The <code><a href=\"api/core/importProvidersFrom\" class=\"code-anchor\">importProvidersFrom</a></code> helper method can be used to collect all providers from any\nexisting NgModule (and transitively from all NgModules that it imports):</p>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nawait <a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a>(RootComponent, {\n  providers: [\n    <a href=\"api/core/importProvidersFrom\" class=\"code-anchor\">importProvidersFrom</a>(SomeNgModule)\n  ]\n});\n</code-example>\n<p>Note: the <code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a></code> method doesn't include <a href=\"api/core/Testability\">Testability</a> by\ndefault. You can add <a href=\"api/core/Testability\">Testability</a> by getting the list of necessary\nproviders using <code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/provideProtractorTestingSupport\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideProtractorTestingSupport</a>()</code> function and adding them into the <code>providers</code>\narray, for example:</p>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nimport {<a href=\"api/platform-browser/provideProtractorTestingSupport\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideProtractorTestingSupport</a>} from '\n@angular /platform-browser';\n\nawait <a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a>(RootComponent, {providers: [<a href=\"api/platform-browser/provideProtractorTestingSupport\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideProtractorTestingSupport</a>()]});\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core/Testability\n - api/core/importProvidersFrom\n - api/platform-browser\n - api/platform-browser/ApplicationConfig\n - api/platform-browser/provideProtractorTestingSupport\n - guide/standalone-components\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/ApplicationRef\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Testability\n - api/core/Type\n - api/core/importProvidersFrom\n - api/platform-browser\n - api/platform-browser/ApplicationConfig\n - api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication#bootstrapapplication\n - api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication#usage-notes\n - api/platform-browser/provideProtractorTestingSupport\n - guide/releases#developer-preview\n - guide/standalone-components\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/platform-browser/src/browser.ts?message=docs(platform-browser)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L40-L129\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/14.1.0-next.0/packages/platform-browser/src/browser.ts#L40-L129\n-->"
